    Swap counts

    swap_usagi_counts.Rd

    Swaps the sourceFrequency and counts/counts_validated columns to allow correct sorting in OHDSI Usagi. This is mainly used to help prioritizing mapping to (manually) validated values vs not-validated (device) data.

    Usage

    swap_usagi_counts(concept_group)

    Arguments

    concept_group

    concept group name that will be used to read the file

    Value

    tibble containing the usagi mappings with counts swapped

    Examples

    swapped <- swap_usagi_counts("numericitems_other")
swapped
